reviewText: This video was as boring as going back to DOS based computers. It must have been a Masters program project for a physical therapist.  Definitely not done by a marketing major.
Great info and techniques but video quality appears homemade and not professional.
The quality of the dvd is horrible. Day 1 and it was skipping and stopping. Please make a new one!. Get the book!  Don't waste 40$!!!
Thought this would be a great addition to my workout repertoire.  Instead it seems to be expert to expert DVD, useful for those who teach or serve as personal trainers to use with clients.
